[i]Key word[/i]: [b]getLevelForXP[/b]

Now, a simple mat equation is [b]total = a0+a1+a2+a3+a4+a5+a6+a7+a8+a9+a10+a11+a12+a13+a14+a15+a16+a17+a18+a19+a20;[/b] You can automatically tell this is adding all the data it got from you.

